original: Zetterqvist, Sven Robert Ferdinand, disponent, Åmål, f. 3/2/94 i Uddevalla av J. A. Z. o. Ehsabetih Hult. G. m. Emy Elvira Larsson, d. 41. Barn: Stig, Birgitta (Britta), Tore. — Stud. v. Uddevalla h. a. 1. samt merk. stud. Res. t. Norge, Danm., Finl., Tyskl., Tjeckoslov. o. Österr. Anst. v. ol. föret. 12-15, kamr. v. A-B Sv. Elektromagne-ter i Åmål 16-24, inköpte o. ombild. det 24. Verkst. dir. där sed. 24. Styr:led. i fl. boL, led. av styr. f. Sv. Hand :bank. avd:kont. i Åmål, led. av folksk:styr.
translated: Zetterqvist, Sven Robert Ferdinand, manager, Åmål, b. 3/2/94 in Uddevalla to parents J. A. Z. and Ehsabetih Hult. Married to Emy Elvira Larsson, deceased in 1941. Children: Stig, Birgitta (Britta), Tore. — Studied at Uddevalla high school, followed by notable studies abroad in Norway, Denmark, Finland, Germany, Czechoslovakia, and Austria. Employed by various companies from 1912 to 1915, then served as an assistant manager at A-B Sv. Elektromagneter in Åmål from 1916 to 1924. In 1924, he purchased and restructured the company, becoming its managing director. Held positions on multiple boards, including Swedish Handbank's local branch in Åmål, and served on the school board.
